  {
    "id": "TALK_HUNTER_DOCTOR_SHARE_LIFE_ELIXIR",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "[Blaine copies the recipe on a paper sheet]  If it is true, the only ingredient I lack is elder ginseng.  Could you please bring me some?  This would be a favor I won't forget soon."
